00:29:22.433 --> 00:29:24.053
<i>You're making a mistake.</i>

463
00:29:25.300 --> 00:29:26.862
<i>Jesus Christ!</i>

464
00:29:28.630 --> 00:29:30.498
<i>- Jesus!
- All right.</i>

465
00:29:37.096 --> 00:29:39.302
<i>Is he gonna kill Chibs?</i>

466
00:29:39.560 --> 00:29:41.539
<i>No. he'll-he'll
probably just let him out</i>

467
00:29:41.682 --> 00:29:43.447
<i>when he gets far enough away.</i>

468
00:29:45.374 --> 00:29:46.980
<i>I got a doctor on the way.</i>

469
00:29:48.510 --> 00:29:50.361
<i>He's a client; we're fine.</i>

470
00:30:02.002 --> 00:30:03.427
<i>You remember what you promised?</i>

471
00:30:03.556 --> 00:30:04.710
<i>I know.</i>

472
00:30:05.584 --> 00:30:07.161
<i>I'm sorry this shit landed here.</i>

473
00:30:07.287 --> 00:30:08.207
<i>We ain't even open yet.</i>

474
00:30:08.208 --> 00:30:10.128
<i>and I got an employee with
a bullet in her leg.</i>

475
00:30:10.129 --> 00:30:11.015
<i>I know.</i>

476
00:30:11.126 --> 00:30:12.468
<i>I'm gonna handle it.</i>

477
00:30:12.586 --> 00:30:15.218
<i>How you gonna handle it. more bullets?</i>

478
00:30:16.209 --> 00:30:18.343
<i>Come on. man. it's a club problem.</i>

479
00:30:18.474 --> 00:30:19.999
<i>No. no. it's-it's</i>
<i>your problem.</i>

480
00:30:20.118 --> 00:30:21.421
<i>And now it's my</i> problem.

481
00:30:21.542 --> 00:30:23.622
That's the way this whole
partner thing works. man.

482
00:30:23.623 --> 00:30:24.165
I got it.

483
00:30:24.284 --> 00:30:27.273
And I'm telling you. it's
not gonna happen again.

484
00:30:27.502 --> 00:30:28.518
Okay?

485
00:30:29.208 --> 00:30:31.681
But we both know that's a lie. right?

486
00:30:34.468 --> 00:30:36.509
So. what you saying. man?

487
00:30:37.037 --> 00:30:37.987
You want out?

488
00:30:38.111 --> 00:30:39.288
Yeah. I do.

489
00:30:39.404 --> 00:30:41.793
That's why <i>we</i> got into this. remember?

490
00:30:42.152 --> 00:30:44.418
You got a beautiful wife.
you got two healthy kids...

491
00:30:44.533 --> 00:30:47.408
you need to accelerate the endgame. Jax.

492
00:30:47.850 --> 00:30:50.010
Get away from all the shit
that's trying to kill you.

493
00:30:50.096 --> 00:30:51.584
I know.

494
00:30:53.922 --> 00:30:55.358
I know what I have to do.

495
00:30:55.476 --> 00:30:56.954
And what about the rest of them?

496
00:30:57.204 --> 00:31:00.410
'Cause if Clay set these guys
in motion. brother on brother.

497
00:31:00.618 --> 00:31:04.608
shit. <i>mano.</i> you ain't
got no trust to lean on.

498
00:31:06.747 --> 00:31:09.284
I'm gonna get together
the cash we owe you.

499
00:31:10.629 --> 00:31:12.573
What are you gonna do about Gemma?

500
00:31:13.791 --> 00:31:15.611
Now. that's <i>not</i> your concern. Nero.

501
00:31:15.746 --> 00:31:17.666
You got to be kidding
me with that shit. right?

502
00:31:17.667 --> 00:31:20.953
After all this. I think I
earned a little concern.

503
00:31:24.608 --> 00:31:27.345
Clay lied about her
being run off the road.

504
00:31:27.460 --> 00:31:29.820
She wanted to tell you the truth.
but she got caught up in

505
00:31:29.821 --> 00:31:33.386
- all that stuff going on with Tara...
- She almost killed my kids!

506
00:31:33.515 --> 00:31:35.715
Okay. I'm not saying that
she didn't make a mistake...

507
00:31:35.716 --> 00:31:37.556
but the lie. that was
because she was scared.

508
00:31:37.557 --> 00:31:38.556
Yeah. she should be.

509
00:31:38.683 --> 00:31:39.767
Really?

510
00:31:39.898 --> 00:31:41.258
Well. what are you gonna do. Pres?

511
00:31:41.259 --> 00:31:42.874
You gonna beat the shit out of your mom?

512
00:31:43.457 --> 00:31:45.762
Ain't that been done
enough by your family?

513
00:31:47.009 --> 00:31:47.969
Hey. you know what. bro?

514
00:31:48.009 --> 00:31:49.395
Hey. hey. hey. hey.

515
00:31:49.968 --> 00:31:51.340
You want to be with Gemma?

516
00:31:51.721 --> 00:31:53.476
Be my guest!

517
00:31:54.877 --> 00:31:57.120
She's your problem now.

518
00:31:57.359 --> 00:31:58.763
Partner.

519
00:32:01.297 --> 00:32:02.840
That's a good boy.

520
00:32:04.032 --> 00:32:05.659
That's a good boy.

521
00:32:16.323 --> 00:32:18.158
Could you give us a minute?

522
00:32:18.513 --> 00:32:19.604
Sure.

523
00:32:19.752 --> 00:32:22.041
- I'll be in NICU.
- Okay.

524
00:32:26.626 --> 00:32:28.332
What's the matter. baby?

525
00:32:29.121 --> 00:32:33.216
I got some new information.

526
00:32:38.144 --> 00:32:40.550
Are you gonna tell her. or should I?

527
00:32:44.164 --> 00:32:48.704
I love him so much. baby.

528
00:32:49.376 --> 00:32:51.100
What happened?

529
00:32:55.570 --> 00:32:57.913
No one tried to run me off the road.

530
00:33:00.656 --> 00:33:03.748
When you called last night. I
was getting high with Unser.

531
00:33:04.452 --> 00:33:06.740
I thought I'd be okay to drive.

532
00:33:08.001 --> 00:33:11.426
I just didn't want to miss
my chance to be with them.

533
00:33:14.173 --> 00:33:15.677
I'm sorry.

534
00:33:16.351 --> 00:33:17.609
You're done.

535
00:33:18.383 --> 00:33:22.574
You don't call...
see or come near my kids again.

536
00:33:22.671 --> 00:33:24.979
- Tara. pl...
- Get out!

537
00:34:05.487 --> 00:34:06.908
Get out of the truck.

538
00:34:07.178 --> 00:34:08.222
Get out.

539
00:34:09.087 --> 00:34:10.318
I said get out!

540
00:34:10.608 --> 00:34:11.414
Get out!

541
00:34:16.074 --> 00:34:17.188
Move it.

542
00:34:17.652 --> 00:34:18.917
Move!

543
00:34:20.561 --> 00:34:21.890
Get on your knees.

544
00:34:32.871 --> 00:34:34.269
Hey.

545
00:34:34.832 --> 00:34:37.756
Least you can look me in the
eyes before you kill me.

546
00:34:38.115 --> 00:34:40.158
you Guinea coward.

547
00:34:48.906 --> 00:34:50.125
Shit!

548
00:35:18.923 --> 00:35:21.045
Just tell 'em about Frankie and Chibs.

549
00:35:26.370 --> 00:35:27.672
What about Clay?

550
00:35:28.645 --> 00:35:30.506
We don't know anything yet.

551
00:35:30.760 --> 00:35:32.257
Not until we can prove it.

552
00:35:32.368 --> 00:35:35.207
Until then. he can't know we're on to him.

553
00:35:35.673 --> 00:35:38.538
However this thing unravels with Clay...

554
00:35:38.889 --> 00:35:41.720
it's got to come to the club.

555
00:35:42.099 --> 00:35:43.157
I know.

556
00:35:43.274 --> 00:35:44.594
Do you?

557
00:35:50.918 --> 00:35:53.457
You just bring the guys up to speed.

558
00:35:58.057 --> 00:36:00.874
We gave your detectives everything we had.

559
00:36:01.681 --> 00:36:03.222
I heard.

560
00:36:04.494 --> 00:36:06.195
How's your boy?

561
00:36:07.859 --> 00:36:09.631
He's gonna be fine.

562
00:36:09.795 --> 00:36:12.374
That's...
that's good.

563
00:36:16.409 --> 00:36:18.998
You know. Rita was pregnant.

564
00:36:20.476 --> 00:36:22.560
Seven weeks in.

565
00:36:23.684 --> 00:36:27.502
I don't even know if it was
gonna be a boy or a girl.

566
00:36:28.477 --> 00:36:29.921
Man.

567
00:36:31.757 --> 00:36:33.188
I'm sorry.

568
00:36:33.423 --> 00:36:35.915
The DNA under her nails was inconclusive.

569
00:36:36.042 --> 00:36:39.313
so I can't tie her death to the MC.

570
00:36:40.418 --> 00:36:43.302
So that puts me back at square one.

571
00:36:43.442 --> 00:36:50.117
So anyone who knows anything
is either... dead... or ain't talking.

572
00:36:50.943 --> 00:36:53.640
We don't know any more than you do.

573
00:36:54.986 --> 00:36:58.958
Do you know why Bobby Munson
was released from Federal holding?

574
00:37:00.421 --> 00:37:02.909
That RICO case fall apart?

575
00:37:04.544 --> 00:37:06.607
What RICO case?

576
00:37:06.790 --> 00:37:08.748
Bobby was inside for Georgie Caruso.

577
00:37:08.862 --> 00:37:10.209
Yeah. I get it.

578
00:37:10.320 --> 00:37:12.483
You and Munson gotta keep that secret.

579
00:37:13.551 --> 00:37:15.305
Where is this headed?

580
00:37:16.322 --> 00:37:19.834
That wasn't the
only RICO secret in SAMCRO.

581
00:37:20.690 --> 00:37:23.693
There's somebody else talking to the Feds.

582
00:37:24.120 --> 00:37:27.211
Giving them information on the cartel.

583
00:37:31.061 --> 00:37:33.281
You said we should work together.

584
00:37:35.475 --> 00:37:36.898
What do you want?

585
00:37:37.261 --> 00:37:39.490
I want Frankie Diamonds and anyone else

586
