responsible for killing my
wife and my unborn child.

587
00:37:46.015 --> 00:37:49.407
I know you will find him before I will.

588
00:37:49.544 --> 00:37:51.393
And if I do?

589
00:37:52.019 --> 00:37:56.170
Give him to me. and I
give you the rat at your table.

590
00:38:34.306 --> 00:38:37.038
Do you ever regret coming back?

591
00:38:41.877 --> 00:38:43.844
To Charming?

592
00:38:47.633 --> 00:38:49.010
No.

593
00:38:51.423 --> 00:38:53.788
Sometimes...

594
00:38:54.888 --> 00:38:58.808
I wonder what would
have happened if I never left.

595
00:39:01.268 --> 00:39:03.052
Yeah.

596
00:39:04.961 --> 00:39:07.313
I think about that. too.

597
00:39:09.913 --> 00:39:13.106
I think about all those choices lately.

598
00:39:21.557 --> 00:39:23.509
You want to tell me?

599
00:39:27.354 --> 00:39:31.974
I'm pretty sure Clay was the one
calling the shots with the Nomads.

600
00:39:39.245 --> 00:39:41.329
How do you know that?

601
00:39:41.587 --> 00:39:44.149
We caught up with Frankie.

602
00:39:46.022 --> 00:39:50.163
Clay was using the home invasions
to create a shitstorm.

603
00:39:50.586 --> 00:39:54.839
hoping the noise in and out of the
club would push me out of my seat.

604
00:39:58.217 --> 00:40:00.525
What do you do now?

605
00:40:01.469 --> 00:40:03.858
I gotta prove it.

606
00:40:04.966 --> 00:40:07.184
Let the club make the call.

607
00:40:07.350 --> 00:40:08.948
What call?

608
00:40:09.334 --> 00:40:11.675
To cut him out and kill him.

609
00:40:14.534 --> 00:40:16.742
How do we do that?

610
00:40:17.237 --> 00:40:19.300
I have a plan.

611
00:40:22.042 --> 00:40:24.607
You may not like it.

612
00:40:46.893 --> 00:40:48.577
I got calls in to everybody.

613
00:40:48.687 --> 00:40:51.594
We're gonna find Frankie.
put this shit to bed.

614
00:40:51.749 --> 00:40:54.040
I know.

615
00:40:56.248 --> 00:40:58.166
What'd Pope have to say?

616
00:41:00.248 --> 00:41:02.866
Gave us some good intel
on the second shooter.

617
00:41:04.843 --> 00:41:09.388
My guess is that Frankie hired
black to put us off the truth.

618
00:41:13.543 --> 00:41:15.407
Got some facts straight.

619
00:41:16.474 --> 00:41:17.805
Yeah?

620
00:41:18.498 --> 00:41:19.894
And what's that?

621
00:41:21.602 --> 00:41:24.730
