648
00:43:42.532 --> 00:43:43.596
Then how?

649
00:43:43.718 --> 00:43:45.238
Just tell me.

650
00:43:46.166 --> 00:43:49.555
Clay was the one that
put the Nomads in motion.

651
00:43:49.690 --> 00:43:54.869
The home invasions. attack
on me and Chibs. everything.

652
00:43:55.329 --> 00:43:57.030
My God.

653
00:43:57.198 --> 00:43:59.162
I need proof.

654
00:44:00.815 --> 00:44:03.156
You're gonna get it for me.

655
00:44:05.877 --> 00:44:07.867
What are you talking about?

656
00:44:10.026 --> 00:44:12.535
He'd do anything for you.

657
00:44:13.616 --> 00:44:15.499
Let him in.

658
00:44:16.050 --> 00:44:17.878
Get his trust.

659
00:44:19.041 --> 00:44:21.655
You want me to spy on him?

660
00:44:22.350 --> 00:44:24.948
I want you to be with him.

661
00:44:26.078 --> 00:44:28.313
Sleep with him.

662
00:44:29.305 --> 00:44:32.359
Make him feel like a king.

663
00:44:33.360 --> 00:44:37.865
The dirty secrets will start to
flow just like they always did.

664
00:44:40.054 --> 00:44:42.300
What if I can't do that?

665
00:44:44.263 --> 00:44:47.294
Then get used to living in a brothel.

666
00:44:48.325 --> 00:44:52.732
Because hookers and bangers are
gonna be your only family.

667
00:44:59.126 --> 00:45:03.295
